<br>
Another one that's undervalued in XP groups is the Wrapped Entrophy Serpent Spine.  These are fairly cheap and as long as you can stay close to the mob this is a real agro monster.  This one is not for raids, but excellent for XP groups.  I could have a shaman and wizard unload on a mob once this went off and it never twitched from me.  This and a Frosty was my favourite combo in XP groups until I got into my low 60's and got some &quot;end game&quot; weapons.<br>
<br>
The Silken Whip of Ensnaring is a good one for offhand.  That and a BBoT mainhand for now would hold you well until you get your Frosty.  Then it's Frosty main and your choice for offhand.<br>
